This is a cgi-bin program that is useful with the
ISMAP attribute on the IMG element.
Earlier, but now obsolete, references to this utility included:
<code>http://hoohoo.ncsa.uiuc.edu/docs/setup/admin/Imagemap.html</code>
and
<code>http://hoohoo.ncsa.uiuc.edu/docs/setup/admin/NewImagemap.html</code>
