<dd>A list of W3C Tech Reports, which currently only lists the latest
proposal for standardization of tables as an extension to RFC 1866.
<dt><A HREF="http://www.javasoft.com/JDK-beta/filesinkit/README"><code>http://www.javasoft.com/JDK-beta/filesinkit/README</code></A>
<dd>The extensions to HTML required to access Java(tm) applets, Version
Beta 1.0. Note that the HTML tag changed from <code>APP</code> to <code>APPLET</code> from pre-beta to beta.
<dt><A HREF="ftp://ftp.isi.edu/internet-drafts/"><code>ftp://ftp.isi.edu/internet-drafts/</code></A>
